    "text": "\\begin{aligned}\\mathbf{H}_{k+1}&=\\quad\\mathbf{GraphLayer}[\\mathbf{H}_{k},\\mathbf{A}]\\\\&=\\quad\\mathbf{a}\\left[\\boldsymbol{\\beta}_{k}\\mathbf{1}^{T}+\\boldsymbol{\\Omega}_{k}\\begin{bmatrix}\\mathbf{H}_{k}\\\\ \\mathbf{H}_{k}\\mathbf{A}\\end{bmatrix}\\right],\\end{aligned}\n\\tag{13.28}"
