    "type": "paragraph",
    "source": "deepseek+paddle",
    "confidence": "high",
    "text": "where H is a $D \\times N$ matrix containing the $N$ node embeddings in its columns, $\\mathbf{A}$ is the $N \\times N$ adjacency matrix, $\\boldsymbol{\\beta}$ is the bias vector, and $\\Omega$ is the weight matrix. Show that this layer is equivariant to permutatio"
