    "text": "\\begin{aligned}\n\\mathrm{GraphLayer}[\\mathbf{H}_{k},\\mathbf{A}]{\\bf P}=\\mathrm{GraphLayer}[\\mathbf{H}_{k}{\\bf P},{\\bf P}^{T}\\mathbf{A}{\\bf P}],\n\\end{aligned}\n\\tag{13.29}"
